{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":83,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"他们靠在床上注视着，"},{"SurahNumber":83,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"不信道的人们已获得他们的行为的报酬了吗？"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当天绽裂，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"听从主命，而且宜於听从的时候；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"当地展开，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"并抛其所怀，而且变为空虚，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"听从主命，而且宜於听从的时候；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"人啊！你必定勉力工作，直到会见你的主，你将看到自己的劳绩。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"至於用右手接过功过簿者，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"将受简易的稽核，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"而兴高采烈地返于他的家属；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"至於从背後接受功过簿者，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"将叫苦连天，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"入于烈火之中，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"从前他在家属间原是快乐的，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"他已猜想他绝不会归於主。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"不然，他的主，原是鉴察他的。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"我以晚霞盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"以黑夜及其包罗万象的盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"以圆满时的月亮盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"你们必定遭遇重重的灾难。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他们怎能不信道呢？"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"当别人对他们宣读《古兰经》的时候，他们怎么不叩头呢？"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"不然，不信道的人们，是否认真理的，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"安拉全知道他们心中隐藏的东西，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"故你当以一种痛苦的刑罚向他们报喜，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"惟信道而且行善的人们，将受不断的报酬。"}]}